        A super-simple, arbitrary webhook client
        
        ## Quickstart
        
        Install Webhooks:
        
        ```sh
        pip install podiant-webhooks
        ```
        
        Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:
        ```python
        INSTALLED_APPS = (
            ...
            'webhooks',
            ...
        )
        ```
        
        ## Running tests
        
        Does the code actually work?
        
        ```
        coverage run --source webhooks runtests.py
        ```
        
